    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>When a shader requires an input of a coordinate system or you need to place a procedural object, we can create a null OBJ. In the Render TAB of the null OBJ, turn on<strong> Output transform as render space (RIB/IFD)</strong>. This will output RiCoordinateSystem with the null OBJ's transformation. </p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646740/nullcoordsys.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157816&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646740/nullcoordsys.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157816&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646752\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"nullcoordsys.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646740\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"35db9cc8-6492-4fba-9346-c46f368ac046\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p>To use it in the shader, drag the path of this null OBJ to the shader parameter. For example:</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" height=\"250\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646740/projector.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157816&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=404&amp;height=250\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544646740/projector.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157816&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544646755\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"projector.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544646740\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1c5dc3d3-8844-4ba9-8519-ff92435a29aa\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646740/projector.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157816&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=490&amp;height=303 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544646740/projector.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433157816&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=404&amp;height=250 1x\"></span></p><p> </p>"
    }
